## 封装加载图片的promise  
```js
let loadImg = (src)=>{
    return new Promise((resolve, reject)=>{
        // write your code here
    })
}
```

student_answer:
const image=new Image();
     console.log(image);
     image.onload=()=>{
       resolve(image);
     };
     image.onerror=()=>{
       reject(new Error("Could not load image at"+src));
     }
     image.src=src;

     document.body.appendChild(image);
